column16: Description: This chart shows temperatures recorded by Max Martin's Three Foot Temperature sensor between 15:45 on 9/1/2023 and 12:30 on 9/5/2023. The purpose of this chart is to provide Brian with data collected from a known calibrated sensor, during the times that Brian's sensors were installed within 1 square foot of the calibrated sensor. Brian, this data is in cells H:9994 - H:10365

Description: This graph shows recorded temperatures between 17:30 on 9/4/2023 and 12:30 on 9/4/2023. This data represents the temperatures collected after the Campbell wiring mistake was repaired on the afternoon of 9/4/2023. Prior to the wiring correction, the six foot height and the center benches sensors were swapped in the coding program. The correction in the coding program appears to have corrected the discrepencies in temperature recordings during the day and night.
